casebody.data:
Finelite v. Finelite et al. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. March 31, 1892.) Action by Lena Finelite against Alexander Finelite and others.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and O'Brien and Ingraham, JJ.

No opinion. Motion granted, without costs. See 16 N. Y. Supp. 287.
